{"tid":2032612,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"銅鑼灣各位手足 仲唔走入利園涼冷氣","createTime":"2020-05-24T06:52:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T09:30:59.000Z","uid":191073,"like":318,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"4ced3a6ef4127824d34c735b092d81ae92fde1d1","tid":2032612,"uid":191073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:52:52.000Z","msg":"次次灣仔 銅鑼灣圍捕 利園都係置身事外，果度先係一堆離地有錢人區既平行時空<br />\n<br />\n要攬炒點可以唔拖埋哩班平行時空既人落水等佢地睇下啲手點對各位手足！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">求幫推等大家仲記得利園哩個地方</span>"},{"pid":"2044cd5841a3244912d9b0ef263fea86a31cadee","tid":2032612,"uid":191073,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:54:53.000Z","msg":"推！！！"},{"pid":"fc6aebf6d4c4e90e6d05838ad29f5e1d0c4f1fb0","tid":2032612,"uid":36566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:55:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e25e956355959d2588d36ebdf04a67efe90ce6b","tid":2032612,"uid":36566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:55:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92e45733fd5722b34b7f759e828339f2b2843682","tid":2032612,"uid":304769,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:55:34.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">借個位，連登黑色五毛風向警告</span><br />\n正視聽，<span style=\"color: red;\">國安法唔係攬炒，美國做野先係</span><br />\n<br />\n大家<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好比五毛帶風向去支持國安法，否則會比對家spin成香港人支持國安法</span>。只有<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人強烈反對下通過，美國才有做野的理由</span>。大家小心。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">連登紅色五毛分化警告</span><br />\n宜家班死五毛<span style=\"color: red;\">除左用鬥黃進行分化，仲用扮演移民/留守派黎進行分化</span>，大家請保持獨立思考<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n連登一向錯曬風向，<span style=\"color: red;\">英國點日落都好，香港問題上都係重要持分者</span>，必須engage。<br />\n我地唔係要拉攏政府班奶共狗（例如Dominic Rabb），而係要<span style=\"color: red;\">拉攏英國民意</span>啊。英國係民主國家，民意最重要。英國民意決定stand with Hong Kong/Boycott China，BJ以至成個政府都無得唔跟。<span style=\"color: red;\">宜家武肺英國死左就三萬幾人，正是推動報仇民意好機會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外要借助美國向英國施壓，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">美國有動機（報武肺之仇）同拳頭，加英國有理由（聯合聲明），兩個加埋先容易嚮香港問題做野</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最後大家要幫手簽個聯署支持BNO平權救手足</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fuk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtdLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=bf800acc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong</a>"},{"pid":"7fc542dc6b6fb3e9493e058903eadb79ca40010d","tid":2032612,"uid":187489,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:55:54.000Z","msg":"啲有錢佬仲要通常好街坊look<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24237e863e2d8a68c13862cf9ab0e10ec6865bf5","tid":2032612,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:56:28.000Z","msg":"轉場五毛，冇人五毛，可以收皮喇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2032603\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2032603</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b41e404355a690195009c5fe05d2709bb203971f","tid":2032612,"uid":191073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92e45733fd5722b34b7f759e828339f2b2843682","tid":2032612,"uid":304769,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:55:34.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">借個位，連登黑色五毛風向警告</span><br />\n正視聽，<span style=\"color: red;\">國安法唔係攬炒，美國做野先係</span><br />\n<br />\n大家<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好比五毛帶風向去支持國安法，否則會比對家spin成香港人支持國安法</span>。只有<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人強烈反對下通